---
title: Double Quick Sweet-Soy Chicken & Celery Slaw with Roast Potato Chunks
description: Sweet chilli sauce can be found on so many things, but we’re sure it will be a real standout with this tender chicken.
Enjoy the pops of flavour and the roasted potato with this winning dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65dec8c85a1abdbdbb7a34d5-f37461b0.jpeg
